t Lothian, Escócia, United Kingdom, seu pai, William 'The Lion' King of Scotland, tinha 28 anos e sua mãe, Margaret de Hythus, tinha 30 anos. Ela teve pelo menos 1 filho com Eustace de Vescy. Ela faleceu em 17 de novembro de 1244, em London, Inglaterra, United Kingdom, com 74 anos, e foi sepultada em Ludgate, London, Inglaterra, United Kingdom."},"ro":{"1170–17 November 1244":"1170–17 noiembrie 1244","1170–1244":"1170–1244","1169–1216":"1169–1216","1205–1253":"1205–1253","1143–1214":"1143–1214","1140–1216":"1140–1216","16 May 1205":"16 mai 1205","Aft 14 November 1218":"după 14 noiembrie 1218","1143":"1143","1253":"1253","1140":"1140","1170":"1170","August 1216":"august 1216","1216":"1216","1205":"1205","1214":"1214","4 December 1214":"4 decembrie 1214","1169":"1169","1244":"1244","17 November 1244":"17 noiembrie 1244","Alnwick, Northumberland, England":"Alnwick, Northumberland, England","Scotland":"Scotland","Haddington, East Lothian, Scotland":"Haddington, East Lothian, Scoția, United Kingdom","London, England":"London, Anglia, United Kingdom","Barnard Castle, Durham, England":"Barnard Castle, Durham, England","Stirling, Stirlingshire, Scotland":"Stirling, Stirlingshire, Scotland","Ludgate, London, England":"Ludgate, London, Anglia, United Kingdom"},"ru":{"1170–17 November 1244":"1170 г.–17 ноября 1244 г.","1170–1244":"1170г.–1244г.","1169–1216":"1169г.–1216г.","1205–1253":"1205г.–1253г.","1143–1214":"1143г.–1214г.","1140–1216":"1140г.–1216г.","16 May 1205":"16 мая 1205 г.","Aft 14 November 1218":"после 14 ноябрь 1218 г.","1143":"1143 г.","1253":"1253 г.","1140":"1140 г.","1170":"1170 г.","August 1216":"август 1216 г.","1216":"1216 г.","1205":"1205 г.","1214":"1214 г.","4 December 1214":"4 декабря 1214 г.","1169":"1169 г.","1244":"1244 г.","17 November 1244":"17 ноября 1244 г.","Alnwick, Northumberland, England":"алнвикк, нортумбирланд, Англия","Scotland":"Шотландия","Haddington, East Lothian, Scotland":"хаддингтон, эаст лотян, Шотландия, Великобритания","London, E